Step 1: Start
Step 2: Create File input.txt and open it in read mode
Step 3: Open a file output.txt in write mode
Step 4: Repeat step 5 till end of the file
Step 5: Read Operator, Arguments 1, 2 and the result register
Step 6: If Operator is not '+', go to step 10
Step 7: Write MOV R0, argument 1 to output file
Step 8: Write ADD R0, argument 2 to output file
Step 9: Write MOV result, R0 to output file
Step 10: If Operator is not '*' go to step 14
Step 11: Write MOV R0, argument 1 to output file
Step 12: Write MUL R0, argument 2 to output file
Step 13: Write MOV result, R0 to output file
Step 14: If Operator is not '/' go to step 18
Step 15: Write MOV R0, argument 1 to output file
Step 16: Write DIV R0, argument 2 to output file
Step 17: Write MOV result, R0 to output file
Step 18: If Operator is not '-' go to step 22
Step 19: Write MOV R0, argument 1 to output file
Step 20: Write SUB R0, argument 2 to output file
Step 21: Write MOV result, R0 to output file
Step 22: If Operator is not '=' go to next line
Step 23: Write MOV R0, argument1 to output file
Step 24: Write MOV result, R0 to output file
Step 25: Close the input file
Step 26: Close the output file
Step 27: Stop
